<div align="JUSTIFY" style="font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-size: small;">IPMP enable to recover from network path failures. If a failure occurs in one network link and an alternate link is configured, IP address can fails over. So network access changes automatically from the failed link to the alternate link, providing uninterrupted access to the network. Here is tips to configure IPMP with Ipv6. You need Solaris 8 10/00 as minimum.</span></div><div style="font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-size: small;"><br>
</span> </div><ol><li><div style="font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-size: small;">Verify  the solaris OS release</span></div><div lang="en-US" style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;">#  more /etc/release</span></div><div lang="en-US" style="margin-bottom: 0in;">                         <span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;">Solaris 10 5/08  s10x_u5wos_10 X86</span></div><div lang="en-US" style="margin-bottom: 0in;">           <span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;">Copyright  2008 Sun Microsystems, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.</span></div><div lang="en-US" style="margin-bottom: 0in;">                         <span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;">Use is subject to  license terms.</span></div><div lang="en-US" style="margin-bottom: 0in;">                              <span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;">Assembled 24  March 2008</span></div></li>
<li><div style="font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; font-style: normal; margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-size: small;">In  SPARC system, you must configure the host to have unique MAC address  for each interface.</span></div><div style="font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;"><span lang="en-US"><span style="font-style: normal;">#  eeprom &quot;local-mac-address?&quot;</span></span>&#160;</span></div><div style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;">local-mac-address?=false<span lang="en-US"><span style="font-weight: normal;">&#160;</span></span></span></div><div style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;"><span lang="en-US"><span style="font-weight: normal;"># eeprom &quot;local-mac-address?=true&quot;</span><span style="font-style: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal;">&#160;</span></span></span></span></div><div lang="en-US" style="font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;"><span lang="en-US"><span style="font-style: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal;"># eeprom &quot;local-mac-address?&quot;</span></span></span>&#160;</span></div><div lang="en-US" style="font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0in;"><span style="font-family: Courier New,monospace; font-size: small;">local-mac-address?=true</span></div></li></ol></div>
